{
  "stem": "4513.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to Camp Phillip Morris, our group did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some-- some of the guys were taken out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of the guys who-- who had reached an age or something that-- and didn't have-- weren't labeled priority and who'd been over a number of months, were taken out of our group and sent to another camp where they-- they were-- they were separated out.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what was left was those of us who either were labeled priority-- and I was labeled priority as a platoon sergeant who was expert, my expertise with mine deactivation, so they took me.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went back to-- came back to the States, went to Fort Lewis, Washington for about a month to-- to take intensive training for the invasion of Japan.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were taken out on boats.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were on a ship and we joined the large armada out in the middle of the Pacific on the way to Japan for the invasion.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We told-- we'd been told that they expected to have upward toward-- we were going in the first assault wave [INAUDIBLE]-- and they felt that we would end up with about 60% to 80% casualties on the beach.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they dropped the bomb, and we didn't have to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took us into the-- our group went into the Philippines.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I deactivated our outfit in the Philippines 'cause I was the last, and by that time I was a first sergeant.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we deactivated the outfit there and packed all the records.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they-- and they sent them to Tokyo, or to Japan.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I stayed out there guarding them with one officer [INAUDIBLE] who-- who never said anything to me-- a white officer who never said anything to me.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
